#include<bits/stdc++.h>

using namespace std;

int SUMD(int N)
{
    int S = 0, R;
    
    while(N>0)
    {
        R = N%10;
        N = N/10;
        S = S + R;
    }
    
    return S;
}


int main()
{
    int T;
    cin>>T;
    
    while(T--)
    {
        int A, B, X, C, K = 0;
        cin>>A>>B;
        
        for(int i=A; i<=B; i++)
        {
            X = SUMD(i);
            C = 0;
            
            for(int j=2; j<=sqrt(X); j++)
            {
                if(X%j==0)
                {
                    C++;
                }
            }
            
            if(X!=1)
            if(C==0)
            K++;
            
        }
        
        cout<<K<<endl;
    }
}
